product.name: R17D LED Bulb Light 8FT, 90W T8 LED Tubes, 10000LM, Clean Cover, HO Rotatable End 8FEET 2 Pin Shop Light, 6000K, T8 T10 T12 Fluorescent Light Replacement, Ballast Bypass,Dual-End Powered (6-Pack)
product.description:
Question: Do I need to bypass the ballast for this R17D/HO end tube light?
Answer: Yes, please remove the starter and ballast before Installation.
Question: Is it single end powered or dual end powered?
Answer: It is dual ended power for this 8ft R17D led bulb.
Question: Will it used for outdoor and dimmable?
Answer: No, this 8feet led tube can only used for indoor and non-dimmable.
Question: This is FA8 single pin tube or R17D HO tube?
Answer: This is R17D HO tube and it can rotatable!
Question: Can we replace our T12 fluorescent tube with this R17D HO 8ft led bulb light?
Answer: Yes! It can replace traditional T8 T10 T12 fluorescent bulbs.
product.bullet_points:
• 【V-SHAPED DESIGN】- These 8FT V Shaped LED Light Bulbs give 270 degree lighting with no wasted light, the LED Chip(576PCS SMD2835) is much more than other 2 rows tube (384PCS SMD2835), so it will shed much more light on your products which makes products brighter and better.
• 【ROTATABLE-END】- This R17D/HO LED bulbs have a rotatable end design that can be rotated 180 degrees, so you can turn the illumination direction according to your requirement.
• 【EASY INSTALLATION】 - Just remove or bypass the starter and ballast before installation. It can replace traditional T8 T10 T12 fluorescent bulbs and save up to 60% on your electricity Bill!
• 【Wide Application】 - Widely used in garage, schools, hospitals, factories, warehouses, supermarkets, offices, convenience stores, gas stations, shops, hotels, etc. NOTE: Please install this item away from the radio, remote control door, etc., which may cause EMI.
• 【 2 YEARS WARRANTY】 - As a led lighting manufacturer with more than 20 years experience, we offer 100% Money Back or Exchange for Customer Service Satisfaction. Just contact us if you have any quality issue or questions, we will solve it for you soon!
